<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_438_r1l8">Edler frawe vvir <expan>ſende<ex>n</ex></expan> cʒu <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>Dankwarte<ex>n</ex></expan> Birkner </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_438_r1l9"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> diener <expan>weıſ<ex>er</ex></expan> dıcʒ <expan>br<ex>iefs</ex></expan> mit euch cʒu <expan>rede<ex>n</ex></expan> von <expan>etlıch<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_438_r1l10"><expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> habe wegen als dıe <expan>yecʒund<ex>en</ex></expan> in <expan>ewre<ex>m</ex></expan> geleite <expan>aufgehalte<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_438_r1l11">iſt <expan>worde<ex>n</ex></expan> / Vnd <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> etc ut in <expan>for<ex>ma</ex></expan> meliori </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_438_r1l12"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> ıııj̃ <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> dıe <expan>Palma<ex>rum</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_438" id="218v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Der edeln frawen, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Borsen von Rysemburg
                                <expan>elich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>witib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, pflegerin czu Taust <app><note place="inline"><expan cert="low">d<ex>etur</ex></expan></note></app>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Edler frawe, wir <expan>sende<ex>n</ex></expan> czu
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Dankwarte<ex>n</ex></expan> Birkner, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
                        diener, <expan>weis<ex>er</ex></expan> dicz <expan>br<ex>iefs</ex></expan>,
                        mit euch czu <expan>rede<ex>n</ex></expan> von
                            <expan>etlich<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> habe wegen, als die
                            <expan>yeczund<ex>en</ex></expan> in <expan>ewre<ex>m</ex></expan>
                        geleite <expan>aufgehalte<ex>n</ex></expan> ist
                            <expan>worde<ex>n,</ex></expan> und <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> etc.
                        ut in <expan>for<ex>ma</ex></expan> meliori. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> iiii <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> die
                                <expan>palma<ex>rum</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
